{"tid":1535112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手整合 懷疑公安混入疑點 集中討論","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:58:32.000Z","uid":128304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9eb984c3cfbbd4766fd254a0cc3fa5e28d52261","tid":1535112,"uid":128304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"又話有假記者證, 合理懷疑有假記者...<br />\n但黑狗連委任證都冇...<br />\n用返同一邏輯<br />\n警方鼓勵我地係應該質疑執勤者 <br />\n究竟係咪公安扮, 違反一國兩制, 知法犯法<br />\n<br />\n小小整合一下, 所有公安跨境執法疑點...<br />\n雖然有d疑點弱d又唔記得日子, 但都想嘗試列晒出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">獨特馬步</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/To7VE4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTo7VE4f.jpg&h=afeac3df&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pkgp1x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pkgp1x.gif&h=8e8e8307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">口音/普通話</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2is6MHb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2is6MHb.jpg&h=99abbce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1dxHC0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1dxHC0.png&h=d16ee2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">民警香港警車拍照</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c7Q4ysb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc7Q4ysb.jpg&h=b1d92d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不熟悉香港法例</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ne2RYoC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNe2RYoC.jpg&h=75499563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CLr4j7tNJjE?t=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCLr4j7tNJjE%3Ft%3D11&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=1ddb3281\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CLr4j7tNJjE?t=11</a><br />\n「唔係你歡唔歡迎，根據警隊條例我有權入嚟，而家我暫時唔入嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">樣子身形陸味濃</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD9tfWN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD9tfWN.jpg&h=11520b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ud9tfFH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fud9tfFH.png&h=c4d72b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">配備與傳統不同</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXBfFaY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXBfFaY.png&h=343d9b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教大家一眼就分到係黑警定公安<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506418</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">公安/大陸人喬裝示威者</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bAT52EF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbAT52EF.jpg&h=29a7ee78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dPpyMT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dPpyMT.jpg&h=1f3a707e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大陸式態度 無委任證/喬裝直接執法</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KGfFt7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KGfFt7.png&h=8d64e43f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UK1jnHu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUK1jnHu.png&h=a2ec89c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該仲有好多, 有冇幫手繼續列出整合&hellip;"},{"pid":"1b64ce75f10a5c1c00de8fef620d786168bfab3d","tid":1535112,"uid":128304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"P牌有無得推"},{"pid":"8c7e05491403445c8ea8ca3305f78fae4d3ceafb","tid":1535112,"uid":185552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr